Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.62,0:01:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別讓他們逃了 把吸血鬼全都趕盡殺絕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.24,0:01:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也算是得到預期的結果了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.33,0:02:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過會 我有些事想問您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你想說的事不感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.76,0:02:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以別跟過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請站住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡面是禁止進入的區域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是所屬於日本帝鬼軍吸血鬼殲滅部隊的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.87,0:02:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是殲滅部隊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尉官級別以下也不允許進入
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是做什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37}是小白鼠們的實驗場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼關係吧 在新宿兵中已是人盡皆知了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小白鼠是指
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:03:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用捕獲的吸血鬼的身體做實驗 調查他們的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說是人體實驗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把他們看成人類的話的確是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無所謂了 請讓我進去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了尉官以下的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個也無法入內嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柊家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼身為統帥帝鬼軍的柊家之人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…卻屈身於軍曹這一軍銜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為喜歡軍曹這個稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 對軍中那些無聊的權利之爭沒有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.38,0:03:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為那個姐姐才去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找了您五天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 那還真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些話想要問您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會回答你的 所以快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優還沒有醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅蓮中校您對優做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是想利用優做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您說因為優的黑鬼武裝是特殊的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以讓我把特別調配的藥交給他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我按照您的吩咐這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個暴走是因為這個原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請回答我 中校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會把感情表露出來還真是少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 那麼 要我如何回答你才滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴你什麼都沒做你就會安心了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能 怎麼會什麼都沒做…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那告訴你這是人體實驗你會生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脆弱的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:05:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想在這已經崩潰的世界中生存下去該怎麼做才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何解決掉天啟四騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何殺死吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柊真晝所開發的鬼咒武裝是犧牲了無數人才完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是沒有鬼咒武裝 人類能在這個世界存活下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在可不是說漂亮話的時候 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說你 迷上優了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這表情是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 你們想怎麼樣都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼間的情愛就別過來一一向我匯報了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下 我的問題還…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個藥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五天就會消散了 優那傢伙快醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡他的話就陪在他身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優 差不多該醒醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷上他了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 請快點醒過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.03,0:07:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要撤退了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去救小優
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心情我很明白 不過現在辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:08:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類的慾望是那般地醜陋 纏繞在小優的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何 差不多變得討厭起人類了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭人類 但是也討厭吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你究竟會成為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是非常期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經鬧得夠歡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我閉嘴 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼咒毒素的去除已經完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼淚什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明從成為吸血鬼之後就不曾流過了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 區區人類還真是把我們弄慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷怎麼樣了 米迦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是被傷得最重的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,區區一個新人又無視我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過那個怪物究竟是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說已經擺上上位始祖會的議題了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.93,0:09:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說人類染指了可能使世界毀滅的禁忌研究
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得是叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「終結的熾天使」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽聞這次襲擊新宿的目的也是為了回收那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔？ 那作戰是失敗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為指揮的費里德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在想什麼我們本來就弄不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法判斷是否失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你應該知道什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.61,0:10:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和那個怪物不是認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以克魯魯大人才這麼中意你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百夜米迦勒 你到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不回答的話我們自己調查便是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼人…什麼人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經不是人類了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是什麼人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一看不就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是個醜陋的吸血鬼罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百夜米迦勒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三位始祖 克魯魯·采佩西大人在傳喚您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請您馬上前往「王之間」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 在傳喚你呢 女王的小心肝
Comment: 0,0:00:00.23,0:00:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 與一 快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優君…你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我要說的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得去告訴大家才行 我馬上去叫他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們…大家都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很擔心？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 有事的只有優君一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優君 你已經昏睡了七天了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七天？ 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 所以我現在去告訴大家你醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 大家都沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米迦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還活著的事也不是我在做夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢相信 你真的還…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛哭鬼的房間是在這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是在這呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼好介意的 這種事當然會哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟家人還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優能醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟發生了什麼事事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從中途開始就什麼都不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是你中途說有點睏就睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？ 騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優那時突然昏過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然部隊陷入了全滅的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過那時援軍趕到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由柊暮人中將以及柊深夜少將所率領的涉谷主力部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.10,0:14:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼那群吸血鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了很多除貴族之外的普通吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還活捉了幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 還是被大部分吸血鬼逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想問米迦是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米迦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用顧慮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管米迦是敵是友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他還活著就足夠了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以請告訴我實情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米迦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被吸血鬼帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要從醫院逃走一個人潛入吸血鬼的城市喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在只要知道他還活著就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來扛著他跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他帶去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時先去臨時據點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米迦 小優
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家人嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筱婭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你為我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是指這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…嗯 只是稍微被吸了點血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 笨蛋優
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你終於醒了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好在給他看被吸血鬼咬的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 你不是也被咬了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.83,0:16:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別在醫院裡大吵大鬧的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:16:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 你這傢伙挺有精神的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？ 我為什麼要擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴上這麼說 期間君月還不是很勤奮地在照顧優
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？ 別給我胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什麼時候做過那種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你照顧得可拚命了 君月君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了大家 能讓我說一句嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.71,0:17:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們為我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有就是 全員都活了下來實在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…也全都是託了同伴們的福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂喂 這是還沒有治好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很明顯腦袋被打壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 其實優君從一開始就是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你別再模仿好孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心我揍飛你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 你還可以繼續休養
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給了我們一些時間休假
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休假？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在優的身體恢復之前柊筱婭小隊暫時休息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我們也明白你很想快點去救出米迦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 不能再給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會好好休息的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:19:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去買點喝的過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是君月 很會照顧妹妹的看護達人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,君月君我也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為女孩卻什麼都不會還粗枝大葉的三三也是令人稱奇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也是女孩卻什麼也沒做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是隊長所以沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴們都沒有事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米迦也還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 有那麼多好事眷顧真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你還活著就不能再錯失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米迦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小優
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會把你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會把你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情還真是超乎想像地順利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們人類依舊沉淪在不斷膨脹的貪慾之中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我們吸血鬼還是傲慢地藐視世間一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不這麼認為嗎 我愉快的搭檔君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是冷淡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.09,0:21:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是這邊的研究資料
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了 差點忘記…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,=================OPE=================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:14.46,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I don't want nobody to get killed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:19.12,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I'll come and get you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:22.22,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I am always ready to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:28.20,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}So don't take all of the blame we were all swept away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:32.05,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Don't take all of the weight. You always do
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.16,0:00:35.75,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}There will always be something you cannot control
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:40.29,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}We will overcome. Your salvation has begun
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:46.08,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}No signs, no lights, such a mess all over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:48.26,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Don't kill you hopes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.41,0:00:54.21,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You make me realize who I need
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:56.60,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I'll be there hold on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:58.58,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}They'll change you somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:01:01.84,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}So where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.03,0:01:04.39,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I'll reach you by dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:09.56,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}The shadows appear，Illusions are born
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.33,0:01:13.53,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}The fallen angels you run with don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.65,0:01:18.14,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}It is our pain that makes us all human after all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:21.09,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Torn old sepia photographs show
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:22.95,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Our fragile precious world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.07,0:01:26.71,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Must discard it, respond to the call
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,=================OPC=================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:14.46,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我不願意看到有人被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:19.12,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我將來找尋你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:22.22,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我一直準備與它們抗爭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:28.20,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}所以別一個人承擔過錯 我們都在命運的洪流中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:32.05,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}別一個人把重任扛在肩上 你總會這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.16,0:00:35.75,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}人生不定 總會有些事你無法掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:40.29,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}而我們會克服一切 對你的救濟已經開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:46.08,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}生命跡象為零 抬頭不見星光 腳下遍地混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:48.26,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}然而不要扼殺你的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.41,0:00:54.21,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}你讓我察覺到我心底所求之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:56.60,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我會堅持在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:58.58,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}可曾幾何時你已被他們改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:01:01.84,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}而真正的你今在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.03,0:01:04.39,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我會在黎明前找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:09.56,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}身影浮現 幻影所生
